{"tid":1071085,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Quantic Dream三款遊戲將登陸PC","createTime":"2019-03-21T06:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T18:35:22.000Z","uid":241300,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a20fe34e5ebfc8f1e9462e891647cfedc80f5924","tid":1071085,"uid":241300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:07:31.000Z","msg":"由 Quantic Dream 所開發的好評遊戲《Heavy Rain》、《Beyond: Two Souls》、《Detroit: Become Human》原先皆僅在 PS3、PS4 平台推出，不過現在官方宣布，這 3 款遊戲將會在 PC 平台發行，並由 Epic Games Store 獨佔 1 年。<br />\n<br />\n目前此 3 款遊戲僅預計會在今年內登陸 PC，並無確切的發售日期。而藉由這次將遊戲推廣至 PC 平台，也意味著 Quantic Dream 與 Sony 的長期獨佔合作關係已經結束，未來的作品也很有可能跨多平台推出。<br />\n<br />\n無論是《Heavy Rain》、《Beyond: Two Souls》或是《Detroit: Become Human》，在 PS3、PS4 平台皆有著很高的讚譽，因此這次宣布推出 PC 版，對沒有 PlayStation 主機的玩家而言肯定是個好消息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/03/21/quantic-dreams-games-coming-to-pc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2019%2F03%2F21%2Fquantic-dreams-games-coming-to-pc%2F&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3D6T6zfZKY9%2BYzH6xvUt7sk%3D&h=e704b44d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/03/21/quantic-dreams-games-coming-to-pc/</a>"},{"pid":"f09062a9dad5c30bfb5ef3ce54078afbe7c5d053","tid":1071085,"uid":136186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:14:40.000Z","msg":"獨佔合約完係可以移植返之前嗰啲作品?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a377d563fa11b6acf75efe02a701c73efd4478","tid":1071085,"uid":6140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:21:17.000Z","msg":"正呀喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過又係epic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68795f6d4f7eeed39892b832618f0c48649959fa","tid":1071085,"uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f09062a9dad5c30bfb5ef3ce54078afbe7c5d053","tid":1071085,"uid":136186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1